---
import { homeClasses, homeDerivedClasses } from "../../lib/homeClasses";

const { container, h2, lead, panelP4, bulletItem, dotAmber, cardElevated } = homeClasses;
const { cardP6 } = homeDerivedClasses;
---

<section class="py-12" id="pricing">
  <div class={container}>
    <h2 class={h2}>Pricing</h2>
    <p class={lead}>Simple and straightforward. $50 per card, with a 5-card minimum.</p>

    <div class={`mt-6 ${cardP6}`}>
      <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-amber-950">Payment + approvals</h3>
      <p class="mt-2 text-amber-900/80">
        You receive a written restoration plan first, and <strong class="font-semibold text-amber-950">you approve it before we start any work</strong>.
      </p>
      <ul class="mt-4 space-y-2 text-sm text-amber-900/80">
        <li class={bulletItem}>
          <span class={dotAmber}></span>
          <span><strong class="font-semibold text-amber-950">When you pay:</strong> after you approve the plan and before restoration begins.</span>
        </li>
        <li class={bulletItem}>
          <span class={dotAmber}></span>
          <span><strong class="font-semibold text-amber-950">How you pay:</strong> we’ll include payment options in your plan/invoice so you can choose the easiest method.</span>
        </li>
        <li class={bulletItem}>
          <span class={dotAmber}></span>
          <span><strong class="font-semibold text-amber-950">If you decline:</strong> we’ll return your cards. You cover return shipping; any inspection/handling fees (if applicable) are disclosed before you ship to us so there are no surprises.</span>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class={`mt-6 ${cardP6}`}>
      <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-amber-950">Shipping, tracking, and insurance</h3>
      <p class="mt-2 text-amber-900/80">
        Shipping is the riskiest part of the entire process. We take a conservative approach, and we recommend you do too.
      </p>
      <div class="mt-4 grid gap-4 md:grid-cols-2">
        <div class={panelP4}>
          <p class="font-semibold text-amber-950">Shipping to us</p>
          <ul class="mt-2 space-y-2 text-sm text-amber-900/80">
            <li class={bulletItem}>
              <span class={dotAmber}></span>
              <span>We recommend <strong class="font-semibold text-amber-950">tracked</strong> shipping and strong packaging.</span>
            </li>
            <li class={bulletItem}>
              <span class={dotAmber}></span>
              <span>For high-value cards, consider <strong class="font-semibold text-amber-950">insurance</strong> and signature on delivery.</span>
            </li>
            <li class={bulletItem}>
              <span class={dotAmber}></span>
              <span>We’ll confirm the shipping address and intake details by email before you send anything.</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class={panelP4}>
          <p class="font-semibold text-amber-950">Return shipping</p>
          <ul class="mt-2 space-y-2 text-sm text-amber-900/80">
            <li class={bulletItem}>
              <span class={dotAmber}></span>
              <span>Return shipping is billed <strong class="font-semibold text-amber-950">at cost</strong> with tracking.</span>
            </li>
            <li class={bulletItem}>
              <span class={dotAmber}></span>
              <span>We can add insurance/signature if you want. Tell us your preference.</span>
            </li>
            <li class={bulletItem}>
              <span class={dotAmber}></span>
              <span>We send tracking as soon as your package ships.</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
      <p class="mt-4 text-sm text-amber-900/70">
        Carrier availability varies by destination. If you have a preferred carrier/service level, include it in your initial email.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-8 grid gap-6 lg:grid-cols-2">
      <div class={`${cardElevated} p-8 ring-1 ring-amber-300/60`}>
        <div class="flex items-baseline justify-between gap-4">
          <div>
            <div class="text-5xl font-bold text-amber-950">$50</div>
            <div class="mt-1 text-base font-semibold text-amber-900/80">per card</div>
          </div>
          <div class="paper-panel px-3 py-2 text-sm font-bold text-amber-900">Min. 5 cards</div>
        </div>
        <div class="mt-6 space-y-2 text-amber-900/80">
          <p class="font-semibold">What's included:</p>
          <ul class="ml-4 list-disc space-y-1.5">
            <li>Detailed inspection with magnification and UV light</li>
            <li>Condition report and restoration plan</li>
            <li>Your approval before work begins</li>
            <li>Before and after photos</li>
            <li>Secure return packaging</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <p class="mt-6 text-sm text-amber-900/70">
          Shipping isn't included. You typically pay for sending cards to us; we bill return shipping at cost with tracking. Insurance is available if you want it.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class={cardP6}>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-amber-950">A note about grading</h3>
        <p class="mt-2 text-amber-900/80">
          Some cards are damaged in ways that would make meaningful improvement count as <strong class="font-semibold text-amber-950">alteration</strong> under PSA, BGS, or CGC standards. If that applies to your card, we'll tell you before we do anything.
        </p>
        <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-amber-900/70">
          This service works best for collectors who want to preserve and display cards that got damaged. We don't promise grade improvements.
        </p>

        <div class="my-6 h-px bg-amber-200"></div>

        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-amber-950">How to pack your cards</h3>
        <ul class="mt-3 space-y-2 text-sm text-amber-900/80">
          <li class={bulletItem}>
            <span class={dotAmber}></span>
            <span>Penny sleeve plus semi-rigid holder like a Card Saver, or toploader</span>
          </li>
          <li class={bulletItem}>
            <span class={dotAmber}></span>
            <span>Team bag with no adhesive touching the card</span>
          </li>
          <li class={bulletItem}>
            <span class={dotAmber}></span>
            <span>Bubble wrap + sturdy box</span>
          </li>
          <li class={bulletItem}>
            <span class={dotAmber}></span>
            <span>Include a list of cards and your contact info</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

